1. Get NetworkManager ofc
2. Cd and edit with sudo /etc/NetworkManager/NetworkManager.conf
   1. Sudo vim /etc/NetworkManager/NetworkManager.conf
3. Add this
[device]
wifi.scan-rand-mac-address=no
4. sudo systemctl restart NetworkManager
5. sudo systemctl start wpa_supplicant.service
6. sudo nmcli dev wifi connect "HomePs91" password "1W87L&&7HPSCB1mM" hidden yes
And there u go lol


